1. *Njim* se osećam sigurno. (I feel secure with him.)
2. Ona je uvek u bliskom kontaktu *njim*. (She is always in close contact with him.)
3. *Njim* se ne bavim. (I don't deal with him.)
4. Šta ona misli o *njim*? (What does she think about him?)
5. Ona je zainteresovana za *njim*. (She is interested in him.)
6. Ona je zaboravila *njim*. (She forgot about him.)